title: I Built A Lifespan Club
alternative_titles: I Built the Club of Longevity
I Created the Club of Immortality
summary: I Built A Lifespan Club Manhua Chen Li works at Mo city, he works there every day with no hope to be seen for the future… until one night. Chen Li obtains a special ability, an ability to buy “Time” and “Lifespan” from people, sell “Time” and “Lifespan” and also let things speed up “Time leap” and slow down “exhaustion time”. So he begins to build a top-class “Lifespan club”!
